room_title: Escape room "The Western Saloon Robbery" by Crazy Cat Escape Room in Houston
room_description: After a crazy criminal rampage night, your gang decides to take a break at the old “Spittin’ Horse” Saloon. Free drinks from the scared owner are one thing, but getting the cash from their locked safe - now, that's a whole another story. The crew has managed to call the Sherriff, and he'll arrive in an hour to arrest you. Don't let him catch you!
